Class DefaultModbusByteArrayFieldItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.plc4x.java.base.messages.items.BaseDefaultFieldItem<Byte[]>
      • org.apache.plc4x.java.base.messages.items.DefaultByteArrayFieldItem
        • org.apache.plc4x.java.modbus.messages.items.DefaultModbusByteArrayFieldItem

  • public class DefaultModbusByteArrayFieldItem
extends DefaultByteArrayFieldItem
    default implementation for DefaultByteArrayFieldItem for Usage within Modbus module default ByteOrder is set to BIG_ENDIAN, can be selected on regarding get-method explicitly from user if needed
